strings.Value: "I like it in here. This place calms my soul."
"In such a dark place, my rest will be calm and deep."
"You manage to see something good even in creepy places like this. I admire that about you."
"Which calm you talkin' about, for demons' sake! I feel danger! My blood is about to boil — and I can almost make out clanging steel!"
"It's a rare occasion when we can learn some optimism from Harrim. Optimism! — From Harrim!"
"I care not where we camp, so long as no one troubles me at night."
